## 2025-12-03
- Added Smart Import workflow with AI-generated mapping plans and bulk conversion into the vault.
- Extended WordItem schema with `source` tracking, auto-migrated legacy data, and surfaced migration toasts.
- Implemented toast notifications for import results and other system messages.
- Enhanced AI service abstraction to support Smart Import planning alongside dictionary fills.
- Built robust import utilities covering CSV, TSV, JSON, and text inputs with duplicate guards.
- Improved text parsing to respect model-provided mappings, promote POS markers into tags, and recover Chinese meanings reliably.
